org.sql: SELECT spree_products.id FROM spree_products INNER JOIN spree_product_properties ON spree_product_properties.product_id = spree_products.id INNER JOIN spree_properties ON spree_properties.id = spree_product_properties.property_id WHERE spree_products.deleted_at IS NULL AND spree_properties.filter_param = "$1" AND spree_product_properties.filter_param IN ("$2", "$3")

rewrites.sql: SELECT spree_products.id FROM spree_products INNER JOIN spree_product_properties ON spree_product_properties.product_id = spree_products.id INNER JOIN spree_properties ON spree_properties.id = spree_product_properties.property_id WHERE spree_products.deleted_at IS NULL AND spree_properties.filter_param = "$1" AND spree_product_properties.filter_param IN ("$2", "$3") LIMIT 1
